+	* Atmel SAMV, SAMS, SAME (Cortex-M7) support
+	* Atmel AT91SAMD handle reset run/halt in DSU, other fixes
+	* Atmel AT91SAML21, SAML22, SAMC20/SAMC21, SAMD09 support
